AiChaos Alpha Chatterbot Module
-------------------------------

Installation:

	Extract the modules to your perl\lib\Chatbot folder.

Usage:

	See the POD data within Alpha.pm.

Example:

	This distribution comes with a test.pl (for testing) and a
	testreply.txt (a simple reply file that tests all the features
	of Alpha).

